import React from 'react'
import { Container,Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Image_card = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
  <Row>
    <Col>1 of 2</Col>
    <Col>2 of 2</Col>
  </Row>
 
</Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default Image_card
